text: The Eyes of Annie Jones is a 1964 British American drama movie directed by Reginald Le Borg and based on the story by Henry Slesar. It stars Richard Conte, Francesca Annis, Joyce Carey, Shay Gorman, Victor Brooks, Mark Dignam, Alan Haines and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1964 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:British drama movies Category:Movies directed by Reginald Le Borg
